Business Brief -- Tandycrafts Inc.:
   Financial Impact of Closing
   A Facility Is Under Review
Tandycrafts, based in Fort Worth, said it expects to
report second-quarter results Jan. 23. In the year-earlier
second quarter, the company reported net income of $1
million, or 41 cents a share.
   Tandycrafts stock was quoted at $17.125, down 12.5 cents,
in late New York Stock Exchange trading yesterday.